      *OET do file
*By Phil Tian
*version 11.2

clear all
cd E:/
capture log close
log using "OET_log", replace
use oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta, clear

gen double ps=psexpectation/1000

*Histogram and kernel density
histogram winpc, bin(15) fcolor(gs12) lcolor(gs16) kdensity by(, legend(on)) by(racenum) by(, title(Histogram of winpc))
graph export histogramkernelwinpc.png, width(2400) height(1800) replace
histogram ps, bin(15) fcolor(gs12) lcolor(gs16) kdensity by(, legend(on)) by(racenum) by(, title(Histogram of ps))
graph export histogramkernelps.png, width(2400) height(1800) replace

*kernel plots of winpc(p) and ps
twoway (kdensity winpc, lcolor(black)) (kdensity ps, lcolor(black) lpattern(shortdash)), by(,title(Kernel Plot-defalut)) by(racenum)
graph export kerneldefault.png, width(2400) height(1800) replace
twoway (kdensity winpc, kernel(gaussian) lcolor(black)) (kdensity ps, kernel(gaussian) lcolor(black) lpattern(shortdash)),by(,title(Kernel Plot-Gaussian)) by(racenum)
graph export kernelgaussian.png, width(2400) height(1800) replace

*kernel plots of transformed winpc(p) and ps
gen double transp=winpc^0.4/(winpc^0.4+(1-winpc)^0.4)
sum transp
twoway (kdensity transp, lcolor(black)) (kdensity ps, lcolor(black) lpattern(shortdash)),by(,title(kernel plots of transformed winpc(p) and ps)) note(gamma=0.4) yscale(range(0 2)) by(racenum)
